text: Ann Mukoro (born 27 May 1975) is a former midfielder. Mukoro played for the Nigeria women's national football team. She played in the 1991 FIFA Women's World Cup and the 1995 FIFA Women's World Cup. ==References== ==Other websites == * Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Nigerian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:1991 FIFA Women's World Cup players Category:1995 FIFA Women's World Cup players
